thread.title: Soap | EastEnders - entertainment.ie

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap | EastEnders - entertainment.ie
text:
Kathy goes ahead and speaks to the police, but what does she want to tell them about? And when DCI Marsden arrives on the Square, who is she looking for this time? Later, Gavin gets wind of Kathy's plan and is furious. Will he follow through with his threats and kill Phil? SO MANY QUESTIONS.
Meanwhile, Abi tries to get to the bottom of Ben's troubles while Paul also tries to talk to Ben but is shut down by him. Elsewhere, Pam makes a huge decision now that she knows the truth about Les and 'Christine'.
